; Coverage for post.cc fn_all with second arg (false)
; When all(EXPR, false) is used, the current posting is excluded from testing
; all(amount > 0, false) returns true for postings where ALL OTHER postings
; in the same transaction have positive amounts

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash     $-10.00

2024/01/02 AllPositive
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Expenses:Rent    $30.00
    Assets:Cash     $-50.00

test reg --limit "all(amount > 0, false)"
24-Jan-01 Test                  Assets:Cash                 $-10.00      $-10.00
24-Jan-02 AllPositive           Assets:Cash                 $-50.00      $-60.00
end test
